replies.body:
first off your wrong in a few things... nidalee was never only top. infact the only time i ever played her top was after the rework but before the AD nerfs.. almost every top lane tanky bruiser counters her top lane. picking her top in the current meta is in her current state is almost asking to lose unless the pick one of the few top laners she can beat like {{champion:8}} {{champion:41}} {{champion:75}} 

nidalee right now is a mid lane assasin who can as of her most recent patch jungle as well. 

as for the lastest nerf to kassadin... yeah thi nerf his ulti range.. not sure if it was needed, maybe it was, maybe it wasn't.. but at lvl 16 it had a 3 second cooldown. so i would have to say a 700 mobilty range skill on a 3 second cooldown is pretty strong. for any character. and they lowered the mana cost of it.
